{"tid":1634302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫手推上熱門］ 克警要求錄音既 終 極 原 因！！！！唔簡單！！","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T14:08:37.000Z","uid":284627,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef9161fee8f502c11b96a00ff8f70c46748b9b2","tid":1634302,"uid":284627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:19:25.000Z","msg":"蘋果今日報：<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191006/60125046?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191006%2F60125046%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=cbf62d3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191006%2F60125046%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=29cb9f18\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191006/60125046?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a></span><br />\n<br />\n其中一段系話：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>他指防暴警要求每人面對鏡頭講述自己的姓名及身份，又要讓警方仔細搜查其隨身物件，「佢要我拎住自己嘅身份證，講今日去過邊，而家搭巴士又係去邊，</strong></span>見到我個袋有條毛巾，就問我點解帶咁多嘢出街，連頂帽都搜得好仔細」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>呢家克警</strong></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><br />\n極度可能 收集緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nVoiceprint / Voice biometrics <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins></span></strong> -</span> <span style=\"font-size: large;\">直譯 系</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 「<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>聲紋</ins></span>」</span></strong> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">姐系你你<strong><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">把聲=你指紋</span></ins></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4cWu2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4cWu2e.jpg&h=63fb1f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為被錄影而影到個樣系大問題 其實 AI 唔止系可以識別<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">人面</span></ins></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>連聲都可以analysis到 然後搵到你系邊個</ins></span></strong></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">只要佢地錄夠一段夠長既錄音就可以</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>呢個技術系 外國勢力 既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府部門</span> <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n開始左被廣泛應用 同埋已用左一段時間 </span></strong>！<br />\n主要 用呢個技術黎</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">核對身份</span></ins></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">例如 系打返去政府部門 補領/報失ID果時 驗證 打電話既人身份，而代替左香港果種 對住個電話 輸入身份證號碼 既方法</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然西方國家 系會問左當事人註唔註冊呢個</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>簡易 認證 服務</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有permission先放落個account度</span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無記錯 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">加拿大</span></strong></span>早系2013, 2014果時已經用緊，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">澳洲</span></strong></span>呢家亦系用緊，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2018年頭有報導指已經擁有 340萬 澳洲人既聲音檔案</span> 大約1/7 人 同意左留聲帶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/knMPP2i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FknMPP2i.jpg&h=c24b6844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">呢家 克警要你拎住身份証講一大堆野，唔止系煩鳩你甘簡單，</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而極有可能 </span> <strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收集埋聲帶落去database</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今次系極有可能收集晒大數據後，日後唔洗拎cam出黎影個樣，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">被監聽後就會 搵到你系邊個</span></strong></span></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n 利申：唔系IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知呢一刻雜音（CCTV既錄影）會有幾大影響到個結果，但準確度一定會愈來愈高。如果巴絲對呢個技術有深入了解，麻煩講多D<br />\n<br />\n利申2：唔洗捉「所謂」錯字，我唔會改到"},{"pid":"e0567b63e748616f1a5144c0328c0ee329acd380","tid":1634302,"uid":284627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:21:27.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"20b836724fe22ba9f6710e5f90bdad18de83c3d8","tid":1634302,"uid":284627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc